                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8697" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0267</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1863 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以E为根：百果园的环境保护实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rooted in E: Environmental Protection Practices at PAGODA</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">崔淼，梁诗露，汪全彦，郑耀洲（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳百果园实业（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百果园；农业企业；环境责任；绿色发展；ESG；2024百优案例；重点项目；系列4-4</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PAGODA, Agribusiness, Environmental Responsibility, Green Development, ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从2020年9月中国提出“双碳”目标开始，一个全新的“E时代”按下了启动键——“E for environment”，环境不仅仅是一种责任，也变得越来越有价值。习近平总书记在党的二十大报告中明确提出，要推动绿色发展，促进人与自然和谐共生。践行绿色发展理念，落实环境责任成为企业实现绿色发展的重要途径。百果园作为农业产业化国家重点龙头企业，将环境保护视为己任，致力于打造一条从种植到零售的绿色生态产业链，为实现农业领域“绿色城市”的理想而不懈奋斗。本案例以ESG背景下，百果园的环境保护实践为主线，详细描述了 百果园以“绿色”为起点，在企业战略的引领下，从绿色组织认同、绿色创新和绿色声誉三方面落实环境责任，构建绿色产业生态圈的全过程。该案例旨在深化学生对企业环境责任理论的学习，掌握ESG视角下环境保护的相关知识，提高学生发掘企业绿色转型中潜在机遇的能力。同时，加强学生对习近平生态文明思想的领悟。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Starting from September 2020, when China put forward its &quot;double carbon&quot; target, a new &quot;E era&quot; has been pressed - &quot;E for environment&quot;, the environment is not only a responsibility, but also becomes more and more valuable. General Secretary Xi Jinping clearly put forward in the report of the 20th Party Congress that we should promote green development and harmonious coexistence between human and nature. Practicing the concept of green development and implementing environmental responsibility has become an important way for enterprises to realize green development. As a national key leading enterprise in agricultural industrialization, PAGODA regards environmental protection as its own responsibility, and is committed to building a green ecological industry chain from planting to retailing, in order to strive for the realization of the ideal of &quot;green city&quot; in the field of agriculture. This case focuses on the environmental protection practice of PAGODA in the context of ESG, and describes in detail the whole process of PAGODA &#39;s building a green industrial ecosystem by taking &quot;green&quot; as the starting point and implementing environmental responsibility from three aspects, namely green organizational identity, green innovation and green reputation under the guidance of its corporate strategy. The case aims to deepen students&#39; understanding of the theory of corporate environmental responsibility, master the knowledge of environmental protection in the ESG perspective, and improve students&#39; ability to explore the potential opportunities in corporate green transformation. At the same time, it strengthens students&#39; comprehension of Xi Jinping&#39;s thought on ecological civilization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《环境、社会及治理（ESG）》、《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）环境责任的内涵和驱动因素；（2）环境责任的践行维度；（3）环境责任的实施路径；（4）环境责任的践行成效；（5）ESG中E的评价指标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
